data.description: This adorable, meticulously maintained 4 bedroom, 2 bath home sits on a hilltop in the quiet neighborhood of Lake Arlington Highlands.  The home features a tandem driveway with a side entry, oversized garage.  Upon entry you will find a spacious, open living, full of natural light from the many windows that run along and wrap around the back of the room and dining area.  The statement piece of the living is a beautiful brick, gas fireplace with a custom mantel and shelving, extending the length of the living room.  The large country kitchen also opens to the living with a large breakfast bar, ready for entertaining.  Relax and enjoy the covered back porch and spacious backyard.  The kitchen is plumbed for gas.  Heating and Air is only 3 years old.  Roof only 6 years old.  This home is full of possibilities!  Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own!
